Who: CYCLONUS
Location: Black Fortress - Security

Cyclonus watched as the energy from Tuscon invaded the base, its power
covereing a signifigant portion of it. It even rolled across the
security section of it, and despite the special safegaurds built in,
managed to penetrate it.

However rather than having a baneful effect, it was rather pleasent.
As it flowed over him he could feel a tingling sensation, followed by
a warm one. He could feel a power within him answer it in like manner,
but differently. His mind was eased for a moment, as if there had been
some internal conflict going on, one that he had not even been aware
of, but one that had now been resolved.

Cyclonus straightened as he relaized what had happened, the last
vestige of Unicron control had been taken aware. No longer did he have
to focus on being loyal to Hydras, or question it, his old loyalty to
Galvatron, or the portion that was in Hydras had been strengthened and
magnified. It was if his purpose in life had been magnified, brought
into focus and sharpened.

So as the screens showed the view outside of the the Maximals, he
smiled as he entered a few commands and watched the world light up, he
was fully a Decepticon once more!

(TAG)

Preston
